OL,3,CM9 crash inquiry finds 'organisational
OL,4,Cfailure' in police call handling
OL,6,FA crashed car lay undiscovered for
OL,7,Fdays with two people inside after an
OL,8,F"organisational failure" in police
OL,9,Fcall handling procedures, a fatal
OL,10,Faccident inquiry has found.
OL,12,FThe inquiry also found a police
OL,13,Fofficer who failed to log a call
OL,14,Freporting the incident was
OL,15,Finadequately trained.
OL,17,FLamara Bell, 25, and John Yuill, 28,
OL,18,Fdied after the car they were in left
OL,19,Fthe M9 near Stirling on July 5, 2015
OL,20,Fas they drove back from a camping trip.
