OL,6,FThey lay in their Renault Clio for
OL,7,Fthree days before being discovered on
OL,8,FJuly 8, despite police previously
OL,9,Fbeing alerted to the incident.
OL,11,FMr Yuill, a father-of-five, was
OL,12,Fpronounced dead at the scene and Ms
OL,13,FBell, a mother-of-two, died four days
OL,14,Flater in hospital.
