OL,3,CM9 crash inquiry finds 'organisational
OL,4,Cfailure' in police call handling
OL,6,FIn his determination published
OL,7,Ffollowing a fatal accident inquiry
OL,8,F(FAI) into the incident, Sheriff James
OL,9,FWilliamson said there was no system of
OL,10,Freconciling information recorded by
OL,11,Fofficers in notebooks with action
OL,12,Ftaken.
OL,14,FHe said: "The failure of Police
OL,15,FScotland to properly risk assess the
OL,16,Fcall handling procedures and have a
OL,17,Fsystem of reconciliation was an
OL,18,Forganisational failure.
