OL,6,F"An organisational failure which led
OL,7,Fto the safety of the public being
OL,8,Fcompromised and to the events of July
OL,9,F5, 2015."
OL,11,FPolice Scotland repeated their apology
OL,12,Fto the families of Mr Yuill and Ms
OL,13,FBell and said that "significant
OL,14,Fimprovements" have been made to call
OL,15,Fhandling systems since 2015, which are
OL,16,Fnow "incomparable" to the systems in
OL,17,Fplace at that time.
