OL,6,FThe inquiry heard Mr Yuill suffered
OL,7,Funsurvivable injuries in the crash but
OL,8,FMs Bell would probably have survived
OL,9,Fif she had received medical treatment
OL,10,Fon July 5, albeit with a long-term
OL,11,Fneurological deficit.
OL,13,FIn his determination, Sheriff
OL,14,FWilliamson noted the Bilston Glen
OL,15,Fpolice call handling centre was under
OL,16,Fpressure that summer amid staffing
OL,17,Fshortages, and there was confusion
OL,18,Famong some officers about the
OL,19,Ftripartite call handling system
OL,20,Fcomprising the Aspire, Avaya and Storm
OL,21,Fsystems.
