OL,3,CM9 crash inquiry finds 'organisational
OL,4,Cfailure' in police call handling
OL,6,FPolice sergeant Brian Henry, now
OL,7,Fretired, volunteered to do overtime at
OL,8,FBilston Glen, arriving into what the
OL,9,Fsheriff described as a "confused,
OL,10,Ffractious working environment".
OL,12,FThe inquiry heard that on July 5 he
OL,13,Ftook a call from farmer John Wilson
OL,14,Freporting a car off the road and
OL,15,Frecorded it in his police notebook,
OL,16,Fbut he failed to log it into the Storm
OL,17,Fcase management system and no action
OL,18,Fwas taken.
