OL,6,FSheriff Williamson found police had
OL,7,Fnot identified the risk that calls
OL,8,Fmight not be dealt with.
OL,10,FHe said: "Brian Henry was inadequately
OL,11,Ftrained and left largely unsupervised
OL,12,Fto operate a system that allowed for
OL,13,Fhuman error to go undetected.
OL,15,F"His human error going undetected
OL,16,Fmeant that Lamara Bell was left in a
OL,17,Fvehicle by the side of a major
OL,18,Fmotorway in Scotland suffering
OL,19,Fdevastating injures.
