OL,6,FSheriff Williamson found the incident
OL,7,Fwas not the result of one individual
OL,8,Ffailure by Police Scotland but "more
OL,9,Fthan one and these failures took place
OL,10,Fover a lengthy period of time, during
OL,11,Fwhich the opportunity to resolve them
OL,12,Fwas lost".
OL,14,FThe FAI came after the family of Ms
OL,15,FBell was awarded more than #1 million
OL,16,Fin damages from Police Scotland in a
OL,17,Fcivil settlement in December 2021.
