OL,6,FIn September 2021, the force was fined
OL,7,F#100,000 at the High Court in
OL,8,FEdinburgh after it pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Fhealth and safety failings which
OL,10,F"materially contributed" to Ms Bell's
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,FSheriff Williamson said Ms Bell's
OL,14,Fsuffering over a period of three days,
OL,15,Fwhen she was severely injured but
OL,16,Fconscious, is "almost
OL,17,Fincomprehensible".
