OL,6,FHe said that since the incident in
OL,7,F2015, the police Contact, Command and
OL,8,FControl Division (C3 Division) has
OL,9,Fbeen transformed into an "efficient,
OL,10,Ftightly-controlled and sophisticated
OL,11,Fcomplex of service centres all capable
OL,12,Fof communicating with each other on a
OL,13,Funified IT network" that is better
OL,14,Fable to serve and protect the public
OL,15,Fthan in 2015.
OL,17,FHe said: "It is not risk-free. It
OL,18,Fstill has a susceptibility to human
OL,19,Ffailure, but the risk of human failure
OL,20,Fand that failure going undetected is
OL,21,Fnow marginal."
