OL,6,FDeputy Chief Constable Alan Speirs
OL,7,Fsaid: "Lamara Bell and John Yuill's
OL,8,Fdeaths were a tragedy and my first
OL,9,Fthoughts today are with their family
OL,10,Fand friends.
OL,12,F"Police Scotland failed Lamara and
OL,13,FJohn in 2015 and I repeat the personal
OL,14,Fapology made previously to their loved
OL,15,Fones. We did not keep them safe in
OL,16,Ftheir time of need as was our duty and
OL,17,Ffor that I am truly sorry.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
