OL,6,F"We have fully participated with all
OL,7,Finspections, investigations and
OL,8,Finquiries established since July 2015
OL,9,Fto identify what went wrong and to do
OL,10,Feverything we possibly can to stop a
OL,11,Fterrible incident such as this being
OL,12,Frepeated.
OL,14,F"Sheriff Williamson's findings
OL,15,Fhighlight the significant improvements
OL,16,Fwhich have been made to our call
OL,17,Fhandling systems. How we respond to
OL,18,F999 and 101 calls now is incomparable
OL,19,Fto how we dealt with them in 2015.
