OL,6,F"None of these provide consolation to
OL,7,FLamara and John's loved ones, but I
OL,8,Fcan give them my assurance that
OL,9,Flessons have been learned and that the
OL,10,Frelentless improvement of service
OL,11,Fdelivery lies at the heart of
OL,12,Feverything we do.
OL,14,F"We are studying the determination in
OL,15,Fdetail for any learning which will
OL,16,Fform part of this continuous
